dct_description_sm: This collection contains shapefiles representing key statistics from the Population and Housing Census of the Dominican Republic in 2010 (Censo Nacional de Población y Vivienda 2010). The original questionairre along with other supporting documentation is included with each download.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_creator_sm: Dominican Republic, Dirección General de Estadística y Censos
